channel.title: [317] Unborn-Pk v1 [317]
channel.description:
[size=18pt]Hello, I'm here today to show you my server development. It's a Stabbingscape v4.1 Base. But what im going to add is listed Below:[/size]
All new areas. 100% anti-null (Not just 1 connection per Ip) Taking Out all Customs. Ticket Reward System Random events, Example, Easter Event Taking out alot of Commands. Fixing Trade Scam (You put 1 item in trade click accept, Then right click it before other person accepts, then when it goes to the second screen, you click remove all) Adding donator Rank Adding Donor Island. Making xp Lamps! (Done!) Making Easter Egg Ring work. (Done!) [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/w1pb1g.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/2n6506u.png[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/n20nsj.png[/img]
[size=24pt]Pictures Coming in a day or 2![/size] [size=18pt]Comment, Good or bad, I Don't care.[/size] [size=24pt]As of right now the credits for the client are 100% to I weed I (not for long), i will code the client once im done with the server.[/size]
